<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.1.4">
<l>iruṭṭiṟ piṟantupō yēḻaival lāyar</l>
<l>maruṭṭait tavirppittu vaṉkañcaṉ māḷap</l>
<l>puraṭṭiyan nāḷeṅkaḷ pūmpaṭṭuk koṇṭa</l>
<l>varaṭṭaṉvan tappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟā</l>
<l rend="indent">ṉammaṉē yappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being born in darkness, preventing the threat to the simple,</l>
<l>strong cowherds, [and] overturning strong Kaṃsa</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [he] died that day,</l>
<l>the fearsome one who took our flowered silks comes</l>
<l>and is making [the face of] a hobgoblin.</l>
<l>Oh! He is making [the face of] a hobgoblin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
